# Serve the standalone Chazarah Map HTML files at the canonical singular
# `/map/<corpus>/<book>/<location>/<lang>` URL (ADR 0002). The files live at
# `public/maps/<corpus>/<book>/<location>/<lang>.html` (plural "maps", with
# extension) so Cloudflare's static asset handler can serve them directly;
# a 200-status rewrite aliases the canonical URL to that file path
# byte-for-byte, with no Astro wrapping (ADR 0004).
/map/:corpus/:book/:location/:lang  /maps/:corpus/:book/:location/:lang.html  200
